HEADWORD: Compt
<hw>Compt</hw> <pr>(kount, <it>formerly</it> k⟦ocr⟧mt; 215)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>compte</ets>. See <er>Count</er> an
